{"word":"G1231 - διαγινώσκω - diaginṓskō - dee-ag-in-o'-sko - Enquire","slug":"G1231","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διαγινώσκω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>diaginṓskō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>dee-ag-in-o'-sko"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Enquire"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B4;&#x03B9;&#x03B1;&#x03B3;&#x03B9;&#x03BD;&#x03C9;&#x0301;&#x03C3;&#x03BA;&#x03C9; - diagino&#x0304;sko&#x0304;</b> - <i>dee-ag-in-o'-sko</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G1097\">G1097</a>; to <i>know thoroughly</i>, that is, <i>ascertain exactly:</i> - (would) enquire, know the uttermost."}]}